TextEng: Could I ask you some questions?
Me have questions, yuh?
Goodbye.
Shieldmeet. What's that?
Why do you think the place "shut down?"
You're sure Desther's back?
What is this place?
Shield-meat. What that be?
Why you think this place "shut down?"
Des-ter back for sure, then, yuh?
Uh... What this place called?
Anything strike you as odd this Shieldmeet?
Shield-meat strike you funny this year?
Which way did he go?
Which way he go?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> "Good man" Desther's a traitor. Lord Nasher sent me to hunt him down.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> '좋은 사람'이라는 데스터는 배신자야. 나셰르 영주님이 그를 추적하라고 날 보냈어.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> That Des-ter guy be evil. Mister Nasher send me to hunt 'im down.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 그 데-스터 나쁜 놈이야. 나셰르 아저씨가 나 보고 잡으라 했어.

TextEng: So you know Desther, do you?
So you know this Des-ter guy, yuh?
Text: 그 데-스터란 사람 아는 거지, 응?

TextEng: How do you know they're not all dead?
Text: 어떻게 그들이 다 죽지 않았다고 아는 거지?

TextEng: How you know they not dead?
